31 // The command status will be used for python script.
32 // use packed attribute so we can unpack it from python and no need to worry about padding.
33 struct __attribute__((packed)) CommandStatus
34 {
35  Protocols::InteractionModel::Status status;
36  chip::ClusterStatus clusterStatus;
37  chip::EndpointId endpointId;
38  chip::ClusterId clusterId;
39  chip::CommandId commandId;
40  uint8_t commandIndex;
41 };
42 
43 static_assert(std::is_same<chip::EndpointId, uint16_t>::value && std::is_same<chip::ClusterId, uint32_t>::value &&
44  std::is_same<chip::CommandId, uint32_t>::value,
45  "Members in CommandStatus does not match interaction_model/delegate.py");
46 static_assert(sizeof(CommandStatus) == 2 + 1 + 2 + 4 + 4 + 1, "Size of CommandStatus might contain padding");
47 
48 struct __attribute__((packed)) AttributePath
49 {
50  chip::EndpointId endpointId;
51  chip::ClusterId clusterId;
52  chip::FieldId fieldId;
53 };
54 
55 static_assert(std::is_same<chip::EndpointId, uint16_t>::value && std::is_same<chip::ClusterId, uint32_t>::value &&
56  std::is_same<chip::FieldId, uint32_t>::value,
57  "Members in AttributePath does not match interaction_model/delegate.py");
58 static_assert(sizeof(AttributePath) == 2 + 4 + 4, "AttributePath might contain padding");
59 
60 struct __attribute__((packed)) AttributeWriteStatus
61 {
62  chip::NodeId nodeId;
63  uint64_t appIdentifier;
64  Protocols::InteractionModel::Status status;
65  chip::EndpointId endpointId;
66  chip::ClusterId clusterId;
67  chip::FieldId fieldId;
68 };
69 static_assert(std::is_same<chip::EndpointId, uint16_t>::value && std::is_same<chip::ClusterId, uint32_t>::value &&
70  std::is_same<chip::FieldId, uint32_t>::value,
71  "Members in AttributeWriteStatus does not match interaction_model/delegate.py");
72 static_assert(sizeof(AttributeWriteStatus) == 8 + 8 + 2 + 2 + 4 + 4, "Size of AttributeWriteStatus might contain padding");
73 
74 extern "C" {
75 typedef void (*PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseStatusCodeReceivedFunct)(uint64_t commandSenderPtr,
76  void * commandStatusBuf,
77  uint32_t commandStatusBufLen);
78 typedef void (*PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseProtocolErrorFunct)(uint64_t commandSenderPtr, uint8_t commandIndex);
79 typedef void (*PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseFunct)(uint64_t commandSenderPtr, uint32_t error);
80 
81 typedef void (*PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnWriteResponseStatusFunct)(void * writeStatusBuf, uint32_t writeStatusBufLen);
82 
83 typedef void (*PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnReportDataFunct)(chip::NodeId nodeId, uint64_t readClientAppIdentifier,
84  uint64_t subscriptionId, void * attributePathBuf,
85  size_t attributePathBufLen, uint8_t * readTlvData,
86  size_t readTlvDataLen, uint16_t statusCode);
87 
88 void pychip_InteractionModelDelegate_SetCommandResponseStatusCallback(
89  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseStatusCodeReceivedFunct f);
90 void pychip_InteractionModelDelegate_SetCommandResponseProtocolErrorCallback(
91  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseProtocolErrorFunct f);
92 void pychip_InteractionModelDelegate_SetCommandResponseErrorCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseFunct f);
93 void pychip_InteractionModelDelegate_SetOnReportDataCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnReportDataFunct f);
94 void pychip_InteractionModelDelegate_SetOnWriteResponseStatusCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnWriteResponseStatusFunct f);
95 }
96 
97 class PythonInteractionModelDelegate : public chip::Controller::DeviceControllerInteractionModelDelegate
98 {
99 public:
100  void OnResponse(app::CommandSender * apCommandSender, const app::ConcreteCommandPath & aPath, const app::StatusIB & aStatus,
101  TLV::TLVReader * aData) override;
102  void OnError(const app::CommandSender * apCommandSender, const app::StatusIB & aStatus, CHIP_ERROR aError) override;
103 
104  void OnAttributeData(const app::ReadClient * apReadClient, const app::ConcreteAttributePath & aPath, TLV::TLVReader * apData,
105  const app::StatusIB & status) override;
106 
107  static PythonInteractionModelDelegate & Instance();
108 
109  void SetOnCommandResponseStatusCodeReceivedCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseStatusCodeReceivedFunct f)
110  {
111  commandResponseStatusFunct = f;
112  }
113 
114  void SetOnCommandResponseProtocolErrorCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseProtocolErrorFunct f)
115  {
116  commandResponseProtocolErrorFunct = f;
117  }
118 
119  void SetOnCommandResponseCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseFunct f) { commandResponseErrorFunct = f; }
120 
121  void SetOnWriteResponseStatusCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnWriteResponseStatusFunct f) { onWriteResponseFunct = f; }
122 
123  void SetOnReportDataCallback(PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnReportDataFunct f) { onReportDataFunct = f; }
124 
125 private:
126  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseStatusCodeReceivedFunct commandResponseStatusFunct = nullptr;
127  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseProtocolErrorFunct commandResponseProtocolErrorFunct = nullptr;
128  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnCommandResponseFunct commandResponseErrorFunct = nullptr;
129  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnReportDataFunct onReportDataFunct = nullptr;
130  PythonInteractionModelDelegate_OnWriteResponseStatusFunct onWriteResponseFunct = nullptr;
131 };
